      "content": "it's just the same every single day. the burning in my legs never actually stops, it just fluctuates. sometimes it's a dull ache and sometimes it feels like being electrocuted while sleeping. i'm just so tired of fighting for a version of life that doesn't even feel like mine anymore. it's like i'm just waiting for the lights to go out so i can finally get some actual rest.",
