    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"the only honest choice\"... that's a heavy way to put it. i guess i just keep thinking about how much easier it would be if there was just... peace. no more meds, no more doctors, no more trying to \"manage\" something that will never go away. does that sound crazy? like i'm just looking for an exit because the room is on fire?",
