      "content": "\"letting the fire do the work\" ... i don't even know if i have the strength left to make a decision like that. it just feels like there's no dignity in this anymore. everyone tells me to keep trying, but they aren't the ones feeling the nerves misfiring every second. do you really think there's any dignity in just... lasting? or is there more peace in just stopping?",
